sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as New Account - Teller - Client
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant AccountS as Account Service
    participant DB_Accts as Accounts DB

    Client->>Gateway: POST /accounts (account details)
    Gateway->>AccountS: Forward create account request
    AccountS->>AccountS: Validate account data
    AccountS->>DB_Accts: Save account information
    DB_Accts-->>AccountS: Account created
    AccountS-->>Gateway: Account creation successful
    Gateway-->>Client: 201 Created (account details)
